<p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">亲爱的小伙伴们，</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">经管学院学生会招新火热开启！</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">在这里，你可以参与策划活动，</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">收获成长，探索无限可能！</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">期待你的加入，一起为经管学生会添彩！</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760964591285.jpg" alt="1760964591285.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760964591285.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p>